### Register User
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Doe",
    "username": "johndoe",
    "password": "password123"
}

### Login User
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Doe",
    "username": "johndoe",
    "password": "password123"
}

### Get Next Question (Authenticated)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/next
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Check Answer (Authenticated)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/answer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "answer": "Option1"
}